<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA624_07_SU_0004_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema624_07.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_07_su_0004">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="2_green" lang="y">하윤이와 승우가 종이띠 600 ㎝를 1 : 3으로 나누어 가지려고 합니다. 두 사람이 나누어 가지는 종이띠는 각각 몇 ㎝인지 구해 봅시다.
      </h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <div class="input_area">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">두 사람이 나누어 가지는 종이띠의 길이는 각각 전체의 몇 분의 몇인지 알아보세요.</h3>

          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <div class="item_box1">
              <div class="name">
                <p lang="y">하윤</p>
              </div>
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA624_07_SU/624_07_0004.png" alt="" />
              <span class="mixed_fraction1">
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1"><math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field></div>
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field></div>
                    +
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field></div>
                  </span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field></div>
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field></div>
                </span>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="item_box2">
              <div class="name">
                <p lang="y">승우</p>
              </div>
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA624_07_SU/624_07_0005.png" alt="" />
              <span class="mixed_fraction1">
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1"><math-field type="number" data-answer-single="3"
                      text-align="center"></math-field></div>
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field type="number" data-answer-single="1"
                        text-align="center"></math-field></div>
                    +
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field type="number" data-answer-single="3"
                        text-align="center"></math-field></div>
                  </span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field type="number" data-answer-single="3"
                      text-align="center"></math-field></div>
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field type="number" data-answer-single="4"
                      text-align="center"></math-field></div>
                </span>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">두 사람이 나누어 가지는 종이띠는 각각 몇 ㎝인가요?</h3>
          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <div class="item_box1">
              <div class="name">
                <p lang="y">하윤</p>
              </div>
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA624_07_SU/624_07_0004.png" alt="" />
              <span class="mixed_fraction1">
                <span>600×</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1"><math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field></div>
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field></div>
                  </span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                  <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="150" text-align="center"></math-field>
                  <span>(㎝)</span>
                </div>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="item_box2">
              <div class="name">
                <p lang="y">승우</p>
              </div>
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA624_07_SU/624_07_0005.png" alt="" />
              <span class="mixed_fraction1">
                <span>600×</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1"><math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field></div>
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field></div>
                  </span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                  <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="150" text-align="center"></math-field>
                  <span>(㎝)</span>
                </div>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnType" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
        <button class="btnReset" lang="y">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck" lang="y">확인</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>

</html>